column5: Hello,Can anyone tell me what the water levels are like and the fishing is like or approximately when the ice went off at Kississing Lake north of Flin Flon. Sorry for the spelling, but I think there is some errors here.Thanks Much for the Info.
Fished there Memorial weekend. Water level down about 1/2 foot. Ice out on May 5. Walleye fishing was great, the northern were a little shy.
